BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//Investment Framework//Routine Schedule//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Investment Framework — Routine Schedule
X-WR-TIMEZONE:UTC
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:routine-1-daily-market-check@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20260615T213000Z
DURATION:PT15M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR
SUMMARY:Routine 1 — Daily Market & Earnings Check
DESCRIPTION:Claude Code Routine 1 (cloxy777/investment-framework).\nChecks 1-day price moves and earnings dates (via yfinance) for every equity holding in portfolio/holdings.md.\nOpens GitHub issues labeled rescore-due for >15% unexplained moves (Rule 9) or earnings releases in the last 2 business days\, pre-filled with whatever yfinance data is available.\nA quiet run with no issues opened is the normal case.\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 1).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:routine-2-weekly-sync-brief@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20260615T110000Z
DURATION:PT15M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO
SUMMARY:Routine 2 — Weekly Portfolio Sync & Brief
DESCRIPTION:Claude Code Routine 2 (cloxy777/investment-framework).\nRuns the full IBKR sync (positions\, cash balances\, active orders) per portfolio/sync-sop.md and commits straight to main.\nPulls the 7-day earnings look-ahead via yfinance\, flags overdue rescore-due issues\, writes sessions/weekly-briefs/YYYY-MM-DD-weekly-brief.md\, and opens/updates the "Weekly Portfolio Brief" issue.\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 2).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:routine-3-quarterly-rate-review@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20260701T120000Z
DURATION:PT15M
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=1,4,7,10;BYDAY=MO,TU,WE,TH,FR;BYSETPOS=1
SUMMARY:Routine 3 — Quarterly Rate Environment Gate Review
DESCRIPTION:Claude Code Routine 3 (cloxy777/investment-framework).\nFetches the current 10Y US Treasury yield from FRED and checks which Rate Regime Modifier band (framework/strategy.md) it falls into versus the last recorded value.\nIf the band changed\, opens an issue + PR (decisions/YYYY-MM-DD-rate-regime-change.md) flagging every holding for /rescore.\nIn January\, also opens the "January annual tasks" checklist (Rate-Normalised PE recalc\, screening coverage\, Q1 framework reviews).\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 3).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:routine-4-screening@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260619T140000Z
DTSTART:20260620T140000Z
DURATION:PT15M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=TU,SA
SUMMARY:Routine 4 — Twice-Weekly Universe Screening Slice
DESCRIPTION:Claude Code Routine 4 (cloxy777/investment-framework).\nRuns /screen with no argument — self-selects the next least-recently-covered slice of framework/screening-coverage-log.md (exactly one slice per run)\, builds the starting universe from quality-factor ETF holdings\, and runs the full Phase 01 quality gate via yfinance.\nUpdates the coverage log\, saves the session log\, opens a PR\, and opens an issue listing any qualified /new-position candidates (or a zero-result issue).\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 4).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:routine-5-monthly-rebalance@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20260706T123000Z
DURATION:PT15M
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYDAY=MO;BYSETPOS=1
SUMMARY:Routine 5 — Monthly Rebalance / Trim Review
DESCRIPTION:Claude Code Routine 5 (cloxy777/investment-framework).\nRuns /rebalance against current holdings — Phase 05 dynamic trimming\, Phase 06 exit triggers\, and the 15% single-position cap (Upgrade 7)\, plus a Turnaround Sub-Gate 2-quarter review check.\nSaves the session log\, opens a PR\, and opens a "Monthly Rebalance" issue with the proposed recycling plan. Proposal only — no trades executed.\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 5).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:manual-freedom-finance-sync@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20260615T120000Z
DURATION:PT1H
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYMONTHDAY=15
SUMMARY:Manual: Sync Freedom Finance portfolio
DESCRIPTION:Not covered by any routine — Freedom24 has no API.\nTake fresh screenshots of the Freedom24 app (Opened Positions view + Accounts/balance view) and run /sync-portfolio (Freedom Finance) in a Claude Code session to refresh portfolio/snapshots/freedom-finance.md and holdings.md.\nDetails: portfolio/sync-sop.md (Freedom Finance Portfolio Sync).
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:manual-q1-annual-review@investment-framework
DTSTAMP:20260613T140000Z
DTSTART:20270115T120000Z
DURATION:PT1H
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=1;BYMONTHDAY=15
SUMMARY:Manual: Q1 annual framework review session
DESCRIPTION:Interactive follow-up to Routine 3's January "annual tasks" checklist issue.\nWork through it with Claude: Rate-Normalised PE recalc for the top 5 holdings\, the annual full-universe re-screen status\, and the Q1 reviews of portfolio/override-log.md\, framework/graveyard-audit.md\, framework/benchmark-comparison.md\, and framework/automation-schedule.md (confirm the IBKR connector and FRED endpoint still work).\nDetails: framework/automation-schedule.md (Routine 3 step 5) and framework/operating-calendar.md.
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
